"parses the operator key using the legacy BLS scheme. The collateral is "
"specified through `collateralHash` and `collateralIndex` and must be an "
"unspent transaction output spendable by this wallet. It must also not be "
"used by any other masternode. This RPC requires a wallet passphrase to be"
" set with walletpassphrase call if wallet is encrypted."
msgstr ""

