"We're not going to validate their [`version` message](../reference/p2p-"
"network-control-messages.md#version) with this simple script, but we will"
" sleep a short bit and send back our own [`verack` message](../reference"
"/p2p-network-control-messages.md#verack) as if we had accepted their "
"[`version` message](../reference/p2p-network-control-"
"messages.md#version)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/examples/p2p-network-retrieving-a-merkleblock.md:82
msgid ""
"We set a [bloom filter](../resources/glossary.md#bloom-filter) with the "
"[`filterload` message](../reference/p2p-network-control-"
"messages.md#filterload). This filter is described in the preceding "
