"[described earlier](../examples/configuration-file.md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/examples/testing-applications.md:69
msgid ""
"Devnets must be assigned both `-port` and `-rpcport` unless they are not "
"listening (`-listen=0`). It is possible to run a devnet on a private "
"(RFC1918) network by using the `-allowprivatenet=1` argument."
