"[`addmultisigaddress` RPC](../api/remote-procedure-calls-"
"wallet.md#addmultisigaddress) instead.  If you add an address to the "
"wallet, you should also make a new backup."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/examples/transaction-tutorial-p2sh-multisig.md:100
