msgid "Governance"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md
msgid ""
"Dash Core synchronizes the governance system via the masternode network "
"as the last stage of the Masternode sync process."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:9
msgid "Synchronization"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:11
msgid ""
"Dash Core synchronizes the governance system via the "
"[masternode](../resources/glossary.md#masternode) "
"[network](../resources/glossary.md#network) as the last stage of the "
"Masternode sync process (following the sync of sporks, the Masternode "
"list, and Masternode payments)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:13
msgid ""
"The [`govsync` message](../reference/p2p-network-governance-"
"messages.md#govsync) initiates a sync of the governance system. "
"Masternodes ignore this request if they are not fully synced."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:15
msgid "There are two distinct stages of governance sync:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:17
msgid ""
"Initial request (object sync) - requests the governance objects only via "
"a [`govsync` message](../reference/p2p-network-governance-"
"messages.md#govsync) sent with a hash of all zeros."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:19
msgid ""
"Follow up request(s) (vote sync) - request governance object votes for a "
"specific object via a [`govsync` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"governance-messages.md#govsync) containing the hash of the object. One "
"message is required for each object. Dash Core periodically (~ every 6 "
"seconds) sends messages to connected nodes until all the governance "
"objects have been synchronized."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:22
msgid ""
"Dash Core limits how frequently the first type of sync (object sync) can "
"be requested. Frequent requests will result in the node being banned."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:25
msgid ""
"Masternodes respond to the [`govsync` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"governance-messages.md#govsync) with several items:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:27
msgid "For Object Sync:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:29
msgid ""
"First, the Masternode sends a [`ssc` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"masternode-messages.md#ssc) (Sync Status Count) for `govobj` objects. "
"This message indicates how many "
"[inventory](../resources/glossary.md#inventory) items will be sent."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:31
msgid ""
"Second, the Masternode sends an [`inv` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"data-messages.md#inv) for the `govobj` and `govobjvote` objects."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:33
msgid "For Vote Sync:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:35
msgid ""
"First, the Masternode sends a [`ssc` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"masternode-messages.md#ssc) (Sync Status Count) for `govobjvote` objects."
" This message indicates how many inventory items will be sent."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:37
msgid ""
"Second, the Masternode sends an [`inv` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"data-messages.md#inv) for the `govobjvote` object(s)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/guide/dash-features-governance.md:39
msgid ""
"Once the syncing [node](../resources/glossary.md#node) receives the "
"counts and inventories, it may request any `govobj` and `govobjvote` "
"objects from the masternode via a [`getdata` message](../reference/p2p-"
"network-data-messages.md#getdata)."
msgstr ""

