msgid ""
"0 - Announce blocks via [`headers` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"data-messages.md#headers) or [`inv` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"data-messages.md#inv)<br>1 - Announce blocks via [`cmpctblock` "
"message](../reference/p2p-network-data-messages.md#cmpctblock)"
msgstr ""

