#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-control-messages.md:352
msgid ""
"The [`sendheaders` message](../reference/p2p-network-control-"
"messages.md#sendheaders) tells the receiving "
"[peer](../resources/glossary.md#peer) to send new "
"[block](../resources/glossary.md#block) announcements using a [`headers` "
