"from a particular point in the [block chain](../resources/glossary.md"
"#block-chain). It allows a [peer](../resources/glossary.md#peer) which "
"has been disconnected or started for the first time to get the "
"[headers](../resources/glossary.md#header) it hasn’t seen yet."
