#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-data-messages.md:374
msgid ""
"The [`getheaders` message](../reference/p2p-network-data-"
"messages.md#getheaders) is nearly identical to the [`getblocks` "
"message](../reference/p2p-network-data-messages.md#getblocks), with one "
"minor difference: the `inv` reply to the [`getblocks` "
"message](../reference/p2p-network-data-messages.md#getblocks) will "
"include no more than 500 [block header](../resources/glossary.md#block-"
"header) hashes; the `headers` reply to the [`getheaders` "
"message](../reference/p2p-network-data-messages.md#getheaders) will "
"include as many as 2,000 block headers."
