"messages.md#govobjvote) is created by a masternode to vote on a "
"governance object (proposal, etc.). When the masternode votes, it "
"broadcasts the [`govobjvote` message](../reference/p2p-network-"
"governance-messages.md#govobjvote) to all its peers."
