"Additionally, nodes can request [`govobjvote` messages](../reference/p2p-"
"network-governance-messages.md#govobjvote) for specific governance "
"objects via a [`govsync` message](../reference/p2p-network-governance-"
"messages.md#govsync). Masternodes ignore requests for votes if they are "
