msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md
msgid ""
"The network messages in this section play a role in controlling Dash's "
"InstantSend feature, utilizing the masternode network for secure and fast"
" transactions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md:9
msgid ""
"The following network messages all help control the InstantSend feature "
"of Dash. InstantSend uses the masternode network to lock transaction "
"inputs and enable secure, instantaneous transactions. For additional "
"details, refer to the Developer Guide [InstantSend section](../guide"
"/dash-features-instantsend.md)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md:11
msgid "clsig"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md:15
msgid ""
"The [`clsig` message](../reference/p2p-network-instantsend-"
"messages.md#clsig) is used to indicate a successful ChainLock for the "
"designated [block height](../resources/glossary.md#block-height). The "
"Chainlock ensures that no other [blocks](../resources/glossary.md#block) "
"can replace the one with the indicated block hash. This determination is "
"made by agreement of a [Long-Living Masternode "
"Quorum](../resources/glossary.md#long-living-masternode-quorum) (LLMQ) "
"which creates the BLS signature in the message."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md:17
msgid ""
"Once a [`clsig` message](../reference/p2p-network-instantsend-"
"messages.md#clsig) is received, clients must reject any other blocks for "
"the indicated block height as described in [DIP8 "
"(ChainLocks)](https://github.com/dashpay/dips/blob/master/dip-0008.md). "
"This increases security by preventing reorganization of a block with a "
"ChainLock (and all blocks below it)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md
msgid "nHeight"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md
#: ../../docs/core/reference/transactions-special-transactions.md
msgid "CBLSSignature"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/core/reference/p2p-network-instantsend-messages.md
msgid ""
"LLMQ BLS signature<br>**Note**: serialized using the basic BLS scheme "
"after Dash 19.0 activation"
msgstr ""

