"messages.md#qjustify) is used to respond to complaints. This provides a "
"way for [nodes](../resources/glossary.md#node) that have been complained "
"about to offer proof of correct behavior. If a valid justification is not"
" provided, all other nodes mark it as a bad. If a valid justification is "
"provided, the complaining node is marked as bad instead (since it "
"submitted a bad complaint)."
