msgid ""
"Previously, ``protx update_registrar_legacy`` could be used to register a"
" masternode with a legacy scheme BLS key. The legacy commands were "
"deprecated as of Dash Core v23.0, so it is now recommended to generate a "
"new basic scheme BLS key instead. This can be done by following the "
":ref:`Generate a BLS key pair <bls-generation>` instructions."
