#: ../../docs/user/network/electrumx-server.rst:11
msgid ""
"ElectrumX is a lightweight Electrum server written in Python that "
"supports a variety of cryptocurrencies including Dash. It provides the "
"backend services necessary to support the :ref:`Dash Electrum wallet "
"<dash-electrum-wallet>`."
msgstr ""

