msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user/wallets/dashcore/coinjoin-instantsend.rst:288
msgid "and many more..."
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user/wallets/dashcore/coinjoin-instantsend.rst:290
msgid ""
"You can read more about InstantSend theory and processes :ref:`here "
