#: ../../docs/user/wallets/electrum/faq.rst:213
msgid "Can I do bulk payments with Dash Electrum?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../docs/user/wallets/electrum/faq.rst:215
msgid ""
"You can create a transaction with several outputs. In the GUI, type each "
